                                    <p class="s_tit">Pledge to practice</p>
                                    <div class="s_con">
                                        <div class="sub">I pledge to actively participate in the operation of the “Compliance Program” to practice fair competition and transparent management, 
                                            and I will do my best to establish a culture of fair trade voluntary compliance within the company.</div>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>I recognize that the voluntary compliance with fair trade provides EMC with a competitive edge and will actively practice it.</li>
                                            <li>As an employee of EMC, I will not engage in bid rigging and will never engage in unfair trade practices that abuse my trading position, nor will I unreasonably request technical data, especially in my dealings with business partners.</li>
                                            <li>Based on the principle of good faith, I will faithfully abide by the Fair Trade Act, Subcontract Act, and the Improper Solicitation and Graft Act and I will actively participate in preventive activities.</li>
